# Copy this file to `.env.local` for local development (Next.js loads it automatically).
# `.env.local` is gitignored — never commit secrets.
#
# The current demo uses in-repo synthetic data and does not require API keys to run.
# Uncomment and fill when you wire real services (maps, APIs, auth, etc.).

# NEXT_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_TOKEN=
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=
